reviewText: Beautiful & relaxing! I love it! Great price too.
THIS IS A VERY TRANQUIL AND RELAXING VIDEO AND I FIND I WAS A GOOD CHIOCE IN PICKING THIS ONE!

I started playing this without any music, just all natural sounds.  It's starts off very nicely but downgrades rather quickly.  About mid way thru I can hear a siren in the background, then in another scene I can hear the photographer breathing, then in yet another scene I can clearly hear people talking in the background saying things like "no way"..... Very disappointing.
I hope there are more of these.  It's so relaxing! It would be nice if they had these in a doctor's office.
